      <title>国际能源署称明年全球石油市场将面临百万桶的供应过剩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/global-oil-market-faces-a-million-barrel-glut-next-year-the-iea-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际能源署表示，由于中国需求持续下滑，明年全球石油市场将面临每天超过 100 万桶的过剩，从而缓解中东及其他地区动荡对油价的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/global-oil-market-faces-a-million-barrel-glut-next-year-the-iea-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
